text: Pobeda () is a rural locality (a village) in Tabynsky Selsoviet, Gafuriysky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 4 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 28 km from Krasnousolsky. == References == Category:Rural localities in Gafuriysky District
title: Pobeda, Gafuriysky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
